metadata.name: Willy #0100
metadata.description:
Who does he remind you? ;)


Willy The Cool Boy is a project created with uniqueness in mind. It is a collection of multiple unique expressions and versions of this character. Based on a baseball and inspired also by the movie Castaway with the ball called Wilson. 
The purpose is to illustrate different moods and emotions through Willys face, and in some versions, Willy has different professions, and in others he is made to resemble real life people, some of them my friends and family, and some of them famous or relevant people. Each immage is 4000x4000 pixels and 300dpi. 
Bringing some fun and interesting experiences to the NFT space with beautiful graphics and a unique character.
